# Java Spring Boot Application - CI/CD Practice

**Project**: Student Management System (Spring Boot + Maven)

### Tech Stack
- **Backend**: Java 21 / Spring Boot 3
- **Build Tool**: Maven
- **CI/CD**: Jenkins (Pipeline)
- **Containerization**: Docker
- **Database**: MySQL / H2 (in-memory)

### Features
- REST APIs for Student CRUD operations
- Jenkins Pipeline for Build → Test → Docker Image → Deploy
- Dockerized application

### Prerequisites
- JDK 21+
- Maven
- Docker
- Jenkins (for CI/CD)

### How to Run Locally

```bash
# 1. Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/bisho-r/Java-app.git
cd Java-app

# 2. Run the application
./mvnw spring-boot:run

# Application will start at http://localhost:8080
